Project - Email Application for IT Systems Team
Scope - Limited to contractors post new acquisition
Primary Objective - Generate email addresses and passwords for it-303-forelon server
Maintenance - IT Specialists (303)
Technical Maintenance and Cost Center - SWG-404-Atlanta/GA427
EOL/Support - Internal
IT Support Administrator Specialist Requirement
Task of creating email accounts for new hires.
Application should do the following:
Generate an email with the following syntax: firstname.lastname@department.company.com
Determine the department (sales, development, accounting), if none leave blank
Generate a random String for a password
Have set methods to change the password, set the mailbox capacity, and define an alternate
email address
Have get methods to display the name, email, and mailbox capacity